Li Qing Tong has a bad temper.

581
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,930
I need to educate her.

582
00:24:13,430 --> 00:24:15,010
Enough.

583
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,500
I'm so angry.

584
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:18,490
I'm still angry after a sleep.

585
00:24:18,910 --> 00:24:20,620
You have a bad temper.

586
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:22,610
He did it to save you.

587
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,470
He's gone too far.

588
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:26,290
You guys don't talk to me, I
don't want to care about him.

589
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:29,690
I am an injured person.
Why is the attitude?

590
00:24:30,950 --> 00:24:31,780
Forget about it.

591
00:24:31,870 --> 00:24:33,270
Just apologize to her.

592
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:34,410
I don't.

593
00:24:36,190 --> 00:24:37,410
You guys,

594
00:24:37,550 --> 00:24:39,020
I took the luggage when we came.

595
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:41,130
Why do I have to carry the
luggage when we go back?

596
00:24:41,230 --> 00:24:43,410
Can we not take the tractor?

597
00:24:44,430 --> 00:24:46,620
A very thick snake

598
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:47,670
was at my feet.

599
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:48,420
I was not afraid

600
00:24:48,510 --> 00:24:49,850
in the face of danger.

601
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:51,170
But I was scared to tears.

602
00:24:51,910 --> 00:24:52,890
I didn't cry at first.

603
00:24:53,350 --> 00:24:53,900
Dear,

604
00:24:53,990 --> 00:24:55,460
you can ask me about this,

605
00:24:55,550 --> 00:24:57,000
I have experience.

606
00:24:57,110 --> 00:24:57,910
When I was young,

607
00:24:57,990 --> 00:25:00,460
I also met a very big snake.

608
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:01,540
How did I cope with it?

609
00:25:01,620 --> 00:25:03,190
I forked the snake's heart

610
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:04,340
and pulled it down,

611
00:25:04,430 --> 00:25:04,950
then it died.

612
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:07,730
Don't make me laugh!

613
00:25:09,070 --> 00:25:09,790
You know,

614
00:25:09,870 --> 00:25:10,460
when I was young,

615
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:12,740
your dad went up to your
grandma's house to help out.

616
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:16,480
He saw a very small snake,

617
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:18,980
and then ran away in fear.

618
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:20,610
Liu Feng Xia, I have told you many times

619
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:22,300
that the snake is poisonous.

620
00:25:22,390 --> 00:25:23,580
It has very long teeth.

621
00:25:23,670 --> 00:25:24,540
Thanks to my fast running,

622
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:26,160
or I would have died.

623
00:25:26,910 --> 00:25:28,500
I think the biggest
problem you kids have now

624
00:25:28,580 --> 00:25:31,650
is that you are too far away from nature.

625
00:25:31,750 --> 00:25:33,260
You should climb mountains
and go down rivers frequently.

626
00:25:33,350 --> 00:25:34,060
Do you hear me?

627
00:25:34,150 --> 00:25:35,180
We're down the river.

628
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:36,580
We also caught fish.

629
00:25:36,670 --> 00:25:37,550
Really?

630
00:25:37,750 --> 00:25:39,290
We caught the most fish.

631
00:25:39,670 --> 00:25:41,330
The credit goes to Chen Jun He.

632
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,020
Can you not mention him?

633
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:43,790
Who is he?

634
00:25:43,870 --> 00:25:45,370
Just that bad boy.

635
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:58,610
If Tong goes to college,

636
00:26:00,030 --> 00:26:03,330
I'll think of another way to pay for this.

637
00:26:04,220 --> 00:26:05,650
What can you do about it?

638
00:26:06,670 --> 00:26:08,250
You must not mess around.

639
00:26:09,230 --> 00:26:10,770
You're getting older

640
00:26:10,990 --> 00:26:12,650
and your body can't take it anymore.

641
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:14,050
Our family

642
00:26:14,150 --> 00:26:15,890
counts on you.

643
00:26:16,190 --> 00:26:16,980
Don't worry.

644
00:26:17,070 --> 00:26:18,570
I have it in mind.

645
00:26:19,710 --> 00:26:21,050
Anyhow,

646
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:22,970
we have to let Tong

647
00:26:23,150 --> 00:26:26,170
go to college in pride.

648
00:26:29,550 --> 00:26:30,300
Yes, right here.

649
00:26:30,390 --> 00:26:30,820
Pain here.

650
00:26:30,910 --> 00:26:31,790
Here.

651
00:26:32,190 --> 00:26:34,750
[Math: 86, Language: 92, English: 72,
Integrated Curriculum: 150, Total: 400]

652
00:26:37,110 --> 00:26:38,650
Is this score accurate?

653
00:26:40,510 --> 00:26:41,060
I think

654
00:26:41,150 --> 00:26:42,770
it's accurate.

655
00:26:44,750 --> 00:26:46,010
Four hundred.

656
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:48,010
That's not enough.

657
00:26:48,630 --> 00:26:49,690
Mr Wu,

658
00:26:50,540 --> 00:26:51,810
are there universities

659
00:26:52,670 --> 00:26:54,410
that don't require tuition?

660
00:26:54,870 --> 00:26:56,020
You are now struggling to go to college.

661
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:58,050
You still have time
to think about tuition?

662
00:26:58,150 --> 00:27:00,060
You don't think about the score yet.

663
00:27:00,150 --> 00:27:00,910
If I

664
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:02,610
am qualified to enter college,

665
00:27:03,230 --> 00:27:05,410
are there universities
that don't require tuition?

666
00:27:05,670 --> 00:27:06,620
Normal University.

667
00:27:07,310 --> 00:27:09,610
I remember that there are normal
universities requiring no tuition.

668
00:27:09,990 --> 00:27:11,090
I'll look it up for you later.

669
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:13,730
Do it now.

670
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:25,470
Done.

671
00:27:30,470 --> 00:27:32,330
You fill in all normal universities.

672
00:27:33,150 --> 00:27:34,250
How promising

673
00:27:34,350 --> 00:27:35,570
to be a teacher.

674
00:27:36,950 --> 00:27:38,350
[Normal University Enrolment Form.
Li Qing Tong, Fudan University]

675
00:27:38,350 --> 00:27:39,500
Can you be a little smarter when you lie?

676
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:40,540
I didn't lie.

677
00:27:40,630 --> 00:27:42,970
I applied for Fudan but just
couldn't get in.

678
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:45,250
You really apply for Fudan.

679
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:46,350
I can't get in anyway.

680
00:27:46,430 --> 00:27:47,770
I fill in whatever is the same.

681
00:27:52,450 --> 00:27:54,510
[Lin Yang Teachers College]

682
00:27:55,110 --> 00:27:56,250
What are you doing?

683
00:27:56,390 --> 00:27:58,090
Fill in the same universities as you.

684
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:59,140
Your estimated score is high,

685
00:27:59,230 --> 00:28:00,890
why do you apply for such universities?

686
00:28:01,670 --> 00:28:02,540
Without you,

687
00:28:02,630 --> 00:28:04,490
there is no meaning for
me to go anywhere else.

688
00:28:05,750 --> 00:28:08,210
You are so nice.

689
00:28:14,710 --> 00:28:15,140
Mr Wu.

690
00:28:15,230 --> 00:28:15,460
Thank you.

691
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:16,430
Water, please.

692
00:28:20,190 --> 00:28:21,290
How have you been?

693
00:28:21,910 --> 00:28:22,850
I am OK.

694
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,460
I heard that many people came to see you,

695
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:27,050
but you pretended not to be home.

696
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:28,370
Not many.

697
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:29,730
Just

698
00:28:29,910 --> 00:28:30,810
one person.

699
00:28:31,750 --> 00:28:33,570
Why do you have so few friends?

700
00:28:34,670 --> 00:28:35,570
Where are your parents?

701
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:38,050
My dad is away on business.

702
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:39,380
My mum

703
00:28:39,460 --> 00:28:40,450
went back to her hometown.

704
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:47,630
Are you hungry?

705
00:28:47,950 --> 00:28:48,830
No.

706
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,340
I'm hungry.

707
00:28:51,430 --> 00:28:52,970
I see what you have in your house.

708
00:28:53,190 --> 00:28:54,060
Is that the kitchen?

709
00:28:54,150 --> 00:28:55,030
Yes.

710
00:28:55,470 --> 00:28:56,490
Just wait.

711
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:01,870
[Good luck and prosperity]

712
00:29:03,430 --> 00:29:04,300
Eat it

713
00:29:04,390 --> 00:29:05,270
while it's hot.

714
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,580
Let me tell you, these braised ribs

715
00:29:09,670 --> 00:29:10,980
are made with my family's secret recipe.

716
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:11,860
It can only be passed
on to women, not to men.

717
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:12,830
I learned it secretly from my mother.

718
00:29:12,910 --> 00:29:13,890
Try it.

719
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:18,890
You're shocked, right?

720
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:21,340
It's delicious, right?

721
00:29:21,430 --> 00:29:23,020
I know this look on your face too well.

722
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:24,300
Whoever I make it for, he
will have this expression.

723
00:29:24,390 --> 00:29:25,270
Let me try it.

724
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:33,150
Oh no.

725
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:35,330
I mistook the salt for sugar.

726
00:29:36,870 --> 00:29:39,450
Do you put your salt and your sugar
together?

727
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:41,060
It's okay.

728
00:29:41,150 --> 00:29:42,340
Please eat more rice.

729
00:29:42,430 --> 00:29:43,220
It goes well with rice.

730
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:44,450
A little more salt is acceptable.

731
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:45,620
Better than being hungry.

732
00:29:45,710 --> 00:29:46,770
Please.

733
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:51,910
It's pretty tasty.

734
00:29:54,380 --> 00:29:55,260
Mr Wu.

735
00:29:55,630 --> 00:29:57,570
Please just say what you want to say.

736
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,000
I have nothing to say.

737
00:29:59,750 --> 00:30:01,640
I came here for a free meal

738
00:30:01,910 --> 00:30:02,940
but ended up making the meal.

739
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:04,130
I lost out.

740
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:08,010
You must be very disappointed.

741
00:30:09,430 --> 00:30:10,310
Wu Zhi Xun,

742
00:30:10,990 --> 00:30:12,320
it's your choice

743
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:13,850
whether you take the exam or not,

744
00:30:14,150 --> 00:30:15,530
and whether you do well or not.

745
00:30:15,710 --> 00:30:17,570
There will always be accidents in life.

746
00:30:17,910 --> 00:30:19,330
For example,

747
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:20,390
when I made the ribs today,

748
00:30:21,310 --> 00:30:22,910
I took the salt as sugar.

749
00:30:22,990 --> 00:30:24,500
So I won't make ribs in the future?

750
00:30:24,590 --> 00:30:25,520
Of course not.

751
00:30:25,670 --> 00:30:26,780
I will only be more serious

752
00:30:26,870 --> 00:30:28,600
the next time I make ribs.

753
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:29,700
Right?

754
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:31,970
Do you want me to

755
00:30:32,190 --> 00:30:33,910
take another year?

756
00:30:33,990 --> 00:30:35,610
This is your life.

757
00:30:35,710 --> 00:30:36,500
Wu Zhi Xun,

758
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:38,050
no one can make the decision for you.

759
00:30:38,190 --> 00:30:39,970
Your hope is the most important.

760
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:41,210
But I have to tell you.

761
00:30:41,910 --> 00:30:44,250
You've been studying for over 3,000 days.

762
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:46,290
Studying for another
300 days is easy for you,

763
00:30:46,750 --> 00:30:47,550
isn't it?

764
00:30:47,630 --> 00:30:48,020
I...

765
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:49,450
Stop it.

766
00:30:49,710 --> 00:30:51,010
Come on, eat.

767
00:30:52,910 --> 00:30:53,790
Please.

768
00:30:58,070 --> 00:30:59,090
Eat more rice.

769
00:31:03,710 --> 00:31:05,540
I write letters to each
member of our class.

770
00:31:05,630 --> 00:31:06,610
This is yours.

771
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:08,010
It must be seen.

772
00:31:08,470 --> 00:31:09,490
Collect it.

773
00:31:12,060 --> 00:31:12,940
I'm leaving.

774
00:31:19,930 --> 00:31:22,610
[To: Wu Zhi Xun]

775
00:31:27,020 --> 00:31:27,660
What does it say?

776
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:28,630
How many?

777
00:31:28,990 --> 00:31:31,010
It says that the subscriber
you dialled is busy now,

778
00:31:31,150 --> 00:31:32,140
please redial later.

779
00:31:32,230 --> 00:31:33,700
You keep dialling. It must
be busy at this moment.

780
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:34,690
Right.

781
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:37,020
This line is not good either.

782
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:38,680
The telecommunications
bureau is unreliable.

783
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,490
Can you please stop talking?

784
00:31:40,590 --> 00:31:41,790
Knock it off, you guys.

785
00:31:41,870 --> 00:31:43,140
I got the exam slip number wrong.

786
00:31:43,230 --> 00:31:44,260
Take it easy.

787
00:31:44,350 --> 00:31:45,140
Right.

788
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:46,160
Take it easy.

789
00:31:53,830 --> 00:31:54,710
Is the phone connected?

790
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:57,820
Yes.

791
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:00,220
You...

792
00:32:00,310 --> 00:32:01,250
Let me listen.

793
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:02,380
You move aside.

794
00:32:02,470 --> 00:32:03,380
You turn on the hands-free.

795
00:32:03,470 --> 00:32:04,990
You make me anxious.

796
00:32:05,070 --> 00:32:07,250
Stop talking.

797
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:09,390
The person who announces the scores,

798
00:32:09,470 --> 00:32:10,460
please speak louder.

799
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:10,900
Uncle,

800
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:11,580
that's not a person.

801
00:32:11,670 --> 00:32:12,970
That's a computer.

802
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:19,130
I'll listen again.

803
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:28,500
How about it?

804
00:32:28,590 --> 00:32:29,970
How about it?

805
00:32:30,550 --> 00:32:31,430
Dear,

806
00:32:31,870 --> 00:32:32,920
what's wrong?

807
00:32:33,190 --> 00:32:34,540
Don't scare me.

808
00:32:34,630 --> 00:32:35,810
I have a weak heart.

809
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:39,110
I got a score of 452.

810
00:32:39,190 --> 00:32:40,620
Not 400.

811
00:32:40,710 --> 00:32:41,500
What?

812
00:32:41,590 --> 00:32:43,010
What?

813
00:32:43,190 --> 00:32:45,270
The passing score
for junior college this year is 435.

814
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:46,300
She exceeded it by 15 points.

815
00:32:46,390 --> 00:32:47,470
She's definitely in.

816
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:48,100
You mean

817
00:32:48,190 --> 00:32:49,500
she's going to college?

818
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:50,870
Li Qing Tong!

819
00:32:50,950 --> 00:32:52,610
You're going to college!

820
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,900
Li, our daughter

821
00:32:54,990 --> 00:32:55,660
is going to college.

822
00:32:55,750 --> 00:32:56,730
Dear,

823
00:32:56,990 --> 00:32:59,060
you are so great.

824
00:32:59,150 --> 00:33:00,380
Scared the hell out of me.

825
00:33:00,470 --> 00:33:02,660
I think for sure I won't make it.

826
00:33:02,750 --> 00:33:03,420
Dear.

827
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:05,850
Mum, I passed the college entrance exam.

828
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:12,440
[Li Qing Tong, Examination Slip]

829
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:15,370
Xiao,

830
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:18,130
come down quickly.

831
00:33:21,710 --> 00:33:23,010
Look at this.

832
00:33:30,900 --> 00:33:31,340
Thanks.

833
00:33:31,430 --> 00:33:32,310
You're welcome.

834
00:33:43,770 --> 00:33:43,910
[Daily Necessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

835
00:33:43,910 --> 00:33:44,790
Mum,

836
00:33:44,950 --> 00:33:46,260
I'm in college.

837
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,450
Really?

838
00:33:47,910 --> 00:33:49,340
Show me quickly.

839
00:33:49,430 --> 00:33:50,310
Show me.

840
00:33:50,470 --> 00:33:52,570
Look, it's the letter of admission.

841
00:33:53,150 --> 00:33:54,370
You are so great.

842
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:55,760
Nice.

843
00:33:56,070 --> 00:33:57,110
You did it.

844
00:33:57,190 --> 00:33:57,620
Son,

845
00:33:57,710 --> 00:33:58,430
whatever you want,

846
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,140
I'll buy it for you.

847
00:33:59,230 --> 00:34:00,020
Name it.

848
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,010
Cell phone.

849
00:34:01,230 --> 00:34:02,110
OK.

850
00:34:02,910 --> 00:34:03,420
Hello,

851
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:04,740
is this Li Jin Bu's home?

852
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:05,350
Yes.

853
00:34:05,430 --> 00:34:06,850
Here is your registered letter.

854
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:09,060
Uncle,

855
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:10,530
is there only one letter?

856
00:34:10,790 --> 00:34:11,670
Yes.

857
00:34:14,750 --> 00:34:15,270
Not right.

858
00:34:15,350 --> 00:34:16,650
There should be two letters.

859
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:17,620
Look again.

860
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:19,170
Do you miss it?

861
00:34:21,989 --> 00:34:22,350
[To: Li Jin Bu]

862
00:34:22,350 --> 00:34:22,860
Why is there

863
00:34:22,940 --> 00:34:24,650
only one letter?

864
00:34:31,790 --> 00:34:32,810
Dear?

865
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:35,750
Dear,

866
00:34:36,870 --> 00:34:38,300
I've heated it up for you three times.

867
00:34:38,389 --> 00:34:40,489
Please take some.

868
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:43,219
You don't eat

869
00:34:43,310 --> 00:34:44,699
because you're not in college?

870
00:34:44,790 --> 00:34:46,530
I'm not qualified to eat.

871
00:34:47,580 --> 00:34:48,340
That's not true.

872
00:34:48,429 --> 00:34:50,219
If I don't eat because I'm not in college,

873
00:34:50,310 --> 00:34:51,179
your mother and I

874
00:34:51,270 --> 00:34:52,730
will starve to death.

875
00:34:52,989 --> 00:34:54,810
That's different.

876
00:34:55,830 --> 00:34:58,360
You were all failing
the exam at that time.

877
00:34:58,830 --> 00:35:00,660
Now, people all get into college,

878
00:35:00,750 --> 00:35:02,610
only I don't.

879
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:04,460
It's not that you don't get into college,

880
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:05,980
it's just that you haven't
received the letter of admission.

881
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:07,820
Maybe it is sent to the wrong person.

882
00:35:07,910 --> 00:35:09,100
Impossible.

883
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:11,140
I don't write the wrong address.

884
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:12,540
Take some please.

885
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:13,510
Dad,

886
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:16,330
if I really don't get into college,

887
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:18,330
will you be ashamed?

888
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:20,580
No, I won't.

889
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:22,240
You mustn't think like that.

890
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:26,090
Are you going to college
so that I can feel proud?

891
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:27,180
No.

892
00:35:27,270 --> 00:35:28,260
You're going to college

893
00:35:28,350 --> 00:35:30,650
to get educated.

894
00:35:30,790 --> 00:35:32,300
Later, with a diploma,

895
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:34,010
you can get a good job.

896
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:36,300
Your life will be better.

897
00:35:36,390 --> 00:35:38,140
But a person's life

898
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:39,380
is long.

899
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:41,850
You don't have to go to college.

900
00:35:41,990 --> 00:35:43,270
You go to college.

901
00:35:43,350 --> 00:35:44,460
You're my daughter.

902
00:35:44,550 --> 00:35:47,140
You don't go to college,
you're still my daughter.

903
00:35:47,230 --> 00:35:48,020
You

904
00:35:48,110 --> 00:35:49,060
are unique

905
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:50,610
in my heart.

906
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:52,780
You are always

907
00:35:52,870 --> 00:35:53,980
the smartest,

908
00:35:54,070 --> 00:35:55,300
most beautiful

909
00:35:55,390 --> 00:35:57,090
and sweetest one in my heart.

910
00:35:59,110 --> 00:36:01,170
Dad, you're a good talker.

911
00:36:01,510 --> 00:36:02,410
Come on.

912
00:36:02,590 --> 00:36:03,690
Take some.

913
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,770
What a good girl.

914
00:36:08,350 --> 00:36:09,810
I just

915
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:11,340
want you

916
00:36:11,430 --> 00:36:13,010
to be healthy.

917
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:14,100
I'm only happy

918
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:15,850
if you're happy.

919
00:36:17,670 --> 00:36:18,680
If I ever

920
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:20,880
have a wish again,

921
00:36:21,790 --> 00:36:23,460
I hope you grow up slowly.

922
00:36:23,550 --> 00:36:25,060
I want you to

923
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,650
spend more time with us.

924
00:36:27,630 --> 00:36:30,490
You'll be eighteen soon.

925
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:31,820
You're growing up.

926
00:36:31,910 --> 00:36:34,930
If you leave us in the future,

927
00:36:37,110 --> 00:36:39,410
I will feel sad.

928
00:36:41,510 --> 00:36:43,290
I also hope not to grow up.

929
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:45,340
I just want to stay with
you and my mum forever.

930
00:36:45,430 --> 00:36:46,400
I will never leave.

931
00:36:48,990 --> 00:36:50,650
That I love to hear.

932
00:36:51,390 --> 00:36:52,500
It's coming.

933
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:53,470
It's coming.

934
00:36:53,750 --> 00:36:54,730
What?

935
00:37:00,390 --> 00:37:01,800
It's true.

936
00:37:02,670 --> 00:37:03,500
I can't believe

937
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:04,860
that you put the wrong address.

938
00:37:04,950 --> 00:37:06,020
I told you,

939
00:37:06,110 --> 00:37:07,730
it must have been sent to the wrong place.

940
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:10,130
I'm a college student now.

941
00:37:10,430 --> 00:37:11,140
Kids,

942
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:11,740
let's go.

943
00:37:11,830 --> 00:37:13,140
I'm taking you out for a treat.

944
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:13,710
Hurry up.

945
00:37:13,790 --> 00:37:14,670
Go.

946
00:37:17,510 --> 00:37:20,990
[Letter of Admission]

947
00:37:21,500 --> 00:37:23,470
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

948
00:37:23,470 --> 00:37:24,410
Wu Zhi Xun,

949
00:37:25,110 --> 00:37:27,810
throughout our lives, we will
make many foolish decisions.

950
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:29,380
We will regret one thousand times.

951
00:37:29,470 --> 00:37:30,930
We will be sad ten thousand times.

952
00:37:31,470 --> 00:37:33,650
This one is not worth
mentioning at this moment.

953
00:37:33,870 --> 00:37:35,130
Start over

954
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:36,270
even if it seems

955
00:37:36,350 --> 00:37:37,610
daunting and confusing.

956
00:37:49,170 --> 00:37:54,300
[Lin Yang Teachers College]

957
00:38:14,310 --> 00:38:15,460
We should eat meat

958
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:17,370
that is half fat and half lean.

959
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:19,330
It's no fun to just eat lean meat.

960
00:38:19,470 --> 00:38:20,500
Look at this fatty meat

961
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:21,980
with oil bubbling on top.

962
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:23,730
Dip it full of chilli powder.

963
00:38:26,070 --> 00:38:28,090
Then drink soda.

964
00:38:32,230 --> 00:38:33,650
It's so delicious.

965
00:38:46,350 --> 00:38:48,250
Am I eating too much?

966
00:38:48,990 --> 00:38:50,650
Why don't I pay for this meal?

967
00:38:51,350 --> 00:38:52,860
I already said it's my treat.

968
00:38:52,950 --> 00:38:54,410
Then I'll treat you next time.

969
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,050
It is burning.

970
00:39:08,540 --> 00:39:08,710
[Welcome to Tieyuan Station]

971
00:39:08,710 --> 00:39:09,790
Mum, I'm leaving.

972
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,900
Take care of yourself.

973
00:39:10,990 --> 00:39:12,750
Son, be safe outside.

974
00:39:12,830 --> 00:39:14,220
Don't worry.

975
00:39:14,310 --> 00:39:15,420
Mum.

976
00:39:15,510 --> 00:39:16,450
Take care of yourself.

977
00:39:16,670 --> 00:39:17,660
Mum.

978
00:39:17,750 --> 00:39:18,590
You're going to college.

979
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:19,930
Get your act together.

980
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,820
I'll give you some more money.

981
00:39:22,910 --> 00:39:23,380
No need,

982
00:39:23,470 --> 00:39:25,190
the money from last time is still unspent.

983
00:39:25,270 --> 00:39:26,250
Take it.

984
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:27,860
Shui.

985
00:39:27,950 --> 00:39:29,210
Tong.

986
00:39:30,430 --> 00:39:32,970
I can't let you go.

987
00:39:33,270 --> 00:39:35,570
I can't let you go either.

988
00:39:36,630 --> 00:39:38,090
What are you two doing?

989
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:39,100
It's not like you're never coming back.

990
00:39:39,190 --> 00:39:41,210
Why do you act as if this is the end?

991
00:39:42,790 --> 00:39:43,970
I tell you,

992
00:39:44,470 --> 00:39:45,430
you two are close to each other,

993
00:39:45,510 --> 00:39:46,660
you must take good care of her.

994
00:39:46,750 --> 00:39:48,850
If she loses one pound,
I will be angry with you.

995
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:49,740
Don't worry.

996
00:39:49,830 --> 00:39:51,770
She will only get fatter.

997
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,640
You need to study hard
when you go to college.

998
00:39:54,750 --> 00:39:55,990
It's not easy for you
to get into accounting.

999
00:39:56,070 --> 00:39:57,060
Don't fail to graduate
when the time comes.

1000
00:39:57,150 --> 00:39:58,460
Don't worry.

1001
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,420
You need to watch Qing Tong.

1002
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:01,410
It's better for her to
graduate than anything else.

1003
00:40:03,390 --> 00:40:04,970
Give us a call when you get there.

1004
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,220
Who hasn't checked in yet?

1005
00:40:07,310 --> 00:40:08,490
Hurry up.

1006
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:10,860
Goodbye.

1007
00:40:10,950 --> 00:40:11,900
We need to go now.

1008
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:12,870
Let's check in.

1009
00:40:13,390 --> 00:40:14,700
You'll be back in two months.

1010
00:40:14,780 --> 00:40:15,580
Let's go.

1011
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:15,910
Mum.

1012
00:40:15,990 --> 00:40:16,740
Let's go.

1013
00:40:16,830 --> 00:40:18,450
Hold the bag.

1014
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:19,780
Goodbye.

1015
00:40:19,870 --> 00:40:21,700
Don't forget to call
me when you get there.

1016
00:40:21,790 --> 00:40:23,250
Or I'd be worried.

1017
00:40:25,390 --> 00:40:26,260
Son, be careful out there.

1018
00:40:26,350 --> 00:40:27,690
Mum, bye.

1019
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:29,620
Have a good trip.

1020
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:31,020
Son, take care of yourself.

1021
00:40:31,110 --> 00:40:31,380
Be good.

1022
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:32,730
Mum, bye.

1023
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:40,900
Sister,

1024
00:40:40,990 --> 00:40:42,100
where is Duan Xiao?

1025
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:43,070
He is upstairs looking for something.

1026
00:40:43,150 --> 00:40:44,030
Well.

1027
00:40:50,630 --> 00:40:51,300
Mum,

1028
00:40:51,390 --> 00:40:53,140
do you notice the jersey of mine?

1029
00:40:53,230 --> 00:40:54,570
The red one with number three.

1030
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,090
You're here.

1031
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:04,610
Are you leaving soon?

1032
00:41:04,870 --> 00:41:05,930
In the evening.

1033
00:41:07,750 --> 00:41:09,450
Are you here to see me off?

1034
00:41:10,750 --> 00:41:12,790
Our colleges are in the same city.

1035
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:14,210
We can see each other every day.

1036
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,290
You don't have to see me off.

1037
00:41:18,190 --> 00:41:19,130
Then

1038
00:41:19,230 --> 00:41:20,530
take this.

1039
00:41:21,270 --> 00:41:22,410
Did you buy this?

1040
00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:23,540
How could I afford it?

1041
00:41:23,630 --> 00:41:24,640
I made it myself.

1042
00:41:24,950 --> 00:41:25,850
Really?

1043
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:29,100
But it's the first time I've
done something like this.

1044
00:41:29,190 --> 00:41:31,370
It has the potential to fall apart.

1045
00:41:31,510 --> 00:41:32,390
Impossible.

1046
00:41:32,910 --> 00:41:34,410
It won't fall apart even if I fall apart.

1047
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,780
Then we have a deal.

1048
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:38,020
I'll be angry with you if you lose it.

1049
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:38,660
Don't worry.

1050
00:41:38,750 --> 00:41:39,770
Definitely not.

1051
00:41:40,230 --> 00:41:41,250
Let me put it on you.

1052
00:41:43,670 --> 00:41:44,550
Hua,

1053
00:41:45,790 --> 00:41:48,890
I didn't say those words last time
because I was drunk.

1054
00:41:49,390 --> 00:41:50,450
What words?

1055
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:52,410
I love you.
